    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>General term referring to any of several medium-sized species of cetaceous mammal, usually reserved for species having a shorter and wider snout than others (which are called dolphins).</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
